@page "/"
@using MurderMysteryParty.Services
@inject AdminAuthService AdminAuthService

<PageTitle>Murder Mystery Dinner Party - 1920's SpeakEasy Gala 2026</PageTitle>

<div class="speakeasy-container">
    <div class="invitation-header">
        <h1 class="gatsby-title">Murder Mystery Dinner Party</h1>
        <h2 class="event-subtitle">1920's SpeakEasy Gala 2026</h2>
        <h3 class="date-location">Mar 14, 2026</h3>
        <h3>Silver Serpent Speakeasy</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="invitation-content">
        <div class="art-deco-border">
            <p class="invitation-text">
                <em>Welcome to the past, guys and dolls! Step back in time to the golden age of jazz, glitz, and glamour!</em>
            </p>
            
            <p class="invitation-details">
                You've been invited to rub elbows with the city's most glamorous — and most dangerous — crowd. 
                The Silver Serpent Speakeasy is open for one night only, and before the evening is through, 
                someone's going to end up horizontal. Don your finest flapper dress or sharpest double breasted suit, 
                and get ready to play your part in a whodunit that'll have everyone pointing fingers 
                across the dinner table!
            </p>

            <div class="party-details">
                <h4>What's on the Level Tonight:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>🍸 Prohibition-era mocktails — strictly off the books</li>
                    <li>🍛 A delicious period-appropriate dinner</li>
                    <li>🎷 1920s music and atmosphere</li>
                    <li>🏆 Prizes for best costume and sharpest detective</li>
                    <li>🎭 A murder mystery you won't see coming</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="navigation-section">
                <a href="my-character" class="character-btn">🎭 My Character</a>
                <a href="characters" class="view-all-btn">👥 All Characters</a>
                <a href="floorplan" class="floor-plan-btn">🗺️ Floor Plan</a>
                <a href="notebook" class="notebook-btn">🗒️ Notebook</a>
                @if (AdminAuthService.IsAuthenticated)
                {
                    <a href="admin" class="admin-btn">🛠️ Game Admin</a>
                }
            </div>

            <div class="how-to-play">
                <h4>📜 How to Play</h4>
                <p class="how-to-intro">
                    The game master will unlock each round as the evening progresses — keep an eye on your
                    <strong>🎭 My Character</strong> page, because that's where your orders arrive.
                    Stay in character, work the room, and follow your instructions for each round.
                    New marching orders appear automatically when each round is unlocked.
                    Jot everything down in your <strong>🗒️ Notebook</strong> — a sharp detective never trusts their memory alone.
                </p>

                <div class="round-guide">
                    <div class="round-guide-item">
                        <h5>🎭 Round <strong>1</strong> — Introductions</h5>
                        <p>
                            Work the room as your character. Share your background and goals freely — 
                            but keep your <em>secrets</em> under your hat (unless trading for someone else's). 
                            Your Round 1 instructions tell you exactly who to approach and what to say. 
                            Stick to the script; every line plants a seed for what comes later.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="round-guide-item">
                        <h5>🕵️ Round <strong>2</strong> — Investigation</h5>
                        <p>
                            <strong>Part A (Pre-Murder):</strong> Fresh instructions arrive. Work your marks, 
                            drop your clues, and dig into everyone's stories. Alibis are taking shape. 
                            Motives are bubbling up. Listen more than you jaw.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <strong>Part B (Post-Murder):</strong> Somebody's been bumped off.
                            The <strong>🔬 Forensic Report</strong> unlocks with the hard evidence. Click the buttons in the app 
                            to see the <strong>🔬 Forensic Report</strong> and the <strong>🗺️ Floor Plan</strong>. At the end,
                            the game master will ask for your accusation: <em>who's the killer, and what's their motive?</em>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="round-guide-item">
                        <h5>⚡ Round <strong>3</strong> Part A — The Reveal</h5>
                        <p>
                            Every character spills their true motive, one by one — watch the order on your character page 
                            to know when your number's up. After the last confession, the cat's outta the bag and 
                            you'll know the full story.                            
                        </p>
                        <p class="round-tip">
                            💡 Round <strong>3</strong> Part B - Don't reach for your hat after the final reveal. Stick around — 
                            things are liable to get a little... <em>chaotic</em>. 🎇
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="golden-rules">
                    <h5>🥂 The Golden Rules</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Stay in character.</strong> Names, accents, mannerisms — commit to the bit.</li>
                        <li><strong>Accuse, deflect, and scheme</strong> — but only with what your character actually knows.</li>
                        <li><strong>Trust no one.</strong> Especially the charming ones.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="speakeasy-footer">
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="about">About</a>
            <span class="footer-divider">|</span>
            <a href="admin">Admin</a>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-copy">Silver Serpent Speakeasy © 2026</p>
    </footer>
</div>
